Brand new secure gated complex with three crossovers, prominent exposure and a total of 40 car parks. Featuring direct access / egress from Southern Cross Way, Links Avenue and signage to Southern Cross Way.

Unit 1 has a striking design, NLA of 479m2 comprising a 393m2 approx warehouse with height of approx 7m, two 5m x 5m roller shutters with awning, 160 amps, ground level reception area with amenities and mezzanine office area with NLA 86m2 approx and amenities.

Links Avenue runs adjacent to Kingsford Smith Drive & Cullen Ave allowing direct access to the Gateway Arterial, Brisbane Airport and Port of Brisbane. Links Ave is situated in the heart of the highly sort after TradeCoast suburb of Eagle Farm.

Phone CBRE Marketing Agents Nick Witheriff or Dan Munnich

Located in Eagle Farm this property is in close proximity to Kingsford Smith Drive, The Brisbane Airport & Gateway Motorway.

* Near new 178sqm* boutique office/warehouse

* 88sqm* corporate office accommodation complete with fit out and open plan areas
* Modern kitchenette and bathroom on ground level
* Great natural light, skylight and LED lighting
* Fully gated and secure unit complex
* Excellent location
